"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640318098,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"pMdjzP-mOicn96tAbrPOEA0i7FyVxHK0r6JZg2z_g4c\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xD5536036199a9f23217A7e43A2e7e2ea760C84D7\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"adIaTaoQEIW9_VoEjsrfqRDEHP_WI1skxMLZwjDUevw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9qQaKPNNKrHJp8lowZBTXiI9UifYUPpnLWUhLzPgsqQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"SJCOcFGz7bxuBNS-n-rRd23Yoj9cWetQSLMJUJX5QBacSI7ECqodbcSIR6PiHgj7OW_dqqYKxzPwNZVfWsjwdA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5a4349411e749917c0b8f6916c13d626a3dcfec08fcc6d7a0296ff2a49fd72ac12faf930511445a380fa15538307810237e59dbb7c19daa2fad930cda9cabe3c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"adIaTaoQEIW9_VoEjsrfqRDEHP_WI1skxMLZwjDUevw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9qQaKPNNKrHJp8lowZBTXiI9UifYUPpnLWUhLzPgsqQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi